<h2>8. Data Model</h2>

<p>The application uses <b>4 Dataverse tables</b> with the publisher prefix <code>cr39e_</code>.</p>

<h3>8.1 AI Ideas (<code>cr39e_aiidea</code>)</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>Column Display Name</th><th>Logical Name</th><th>Data Type</th><th>Required</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
<tr><td>Title</td><td>cr39e_title</td><td>Single line of text (200)</td><td>Yes</td><td>Primary name column</td></tr>
<tr><td>Description</td><td>cr39e_description</td><td>Multiple lines of text</td><td>Yes</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td>AI Capability Area</td><td>cr39e_aicapabilityarea</td><td>Choice</td><td>Yes</td><td>8 values (see Section 8.5)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Business Function</td><td>cr39e_businessfunction</td><td>Choice</td><td>Yes</td><td>11 values (see Section 8.5)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Expected Benefits</td><td>cr39e_expectedbenefits</td><td>Multiple lines of text</td><td>No</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td>Submitter Name</td><td>cr39e_submittername</td><td>Single line of text (100)</td><td>No</td><td></td></tr>
<tr><td>Submitter Email</td><td>cr39e_submitteremail</td><td>Single line of text (200)</td><td>No</td><td>Format: Email</td></tr>
<tr><td>Status</td><td>cr39e_status</td><td>Choice</td><td>Yes</td><td>11 values (see Section 7.6). Default: Submitted</td></tr>
<tr><td>Created On</td><td>createdon</td><td>Date and Time</td><td>Auto</td><td>System-managed</td></tr>
</table>

