<h3>8.6 Entity Relationship Diagram</h3>
<div class="callout">
<pre style="font-family: Consolas, monospace; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0;">
 ┌──────────────────┐         ┌────────────────────────┐
 │    AI Ideas      │ 1 ── * │  AI Idea Assessments   │
 │ (cr39e_aiidea)   │         │ (cr39e_aiideaassessment)│
 └──────────────────┘         └────────────────────────┘

 ┌──────────────────┐         ┌────────────────────────┐
 │   AI Prompts     │ 1 ── * │  AI Prompt Ratings     │
 │ (cr39e_aiprompt) │         │ (cr39e_aipromptrating) │
 └──────────────────┘         └────────────────────────┘
</pre>
<p style="margin-top: 6pt; font-size: 10pt;">Each AI Idea can have multiple Assessments (typically one). Each AI Prompt can have multiple Ratings (one per user interaction).</p>
</div>

